  "prompt": "How was your experience of training after clearing SSC CGL?",
  "response": "As an AI, I don't have personal experiences or undergo training like a human would after clearing an exam like the SSC CGL. However, if you're referring to what one might expect after successfully clearing the SSC CGL and starting their training, I can provide some general information.\n\nAfter clearing the SSC CGL exam, candidates are typically allocated to various government departments and undergo training specific to their job roles. This training aims to equip them with the necessary skills and knowledge to perform their duties effectively. The nature and duration of the training can vary depending on the department and the specific role the candidate is selected for. Training often includes workshops, seminars, on-the-job training, and sometimes classroom sessions, focusing on the departmental processes, regulations, and functions.\n\nIf you have specific questions about the training process, feel free to ask!",
